@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Request";
}

<div class="banner-image banner-image-requests"><h1>Speaker Requests</h1>
</div>

<div class="row opening-blurb gx-0">
    <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h3>MSIS 4003</h3>
        <h4>Systems Analysis and Design</h4>
        <h5>Class Type: In-person and Online</h5>
        <p class="me-3"> Students in this course learn the core concepts and skills for developing software in an organizational context. These concepts include agile software development techniques, as well as the socio-cultural aspects of the systems analysis and design process. </p>
        <h5>Speaker Guidelines</h5>
        <p class="me-3"> I am looking for a newer graduate (approximately 1 – 3 years post-grad) who can speak to my classes about the transition from collegiate life to the workplace. I would like to have a speaker who can discuss how they applied what they learned in class to a professional environment. What are some challenges you faced? How much new-hire training did you complete? Did you feel prepared for your role? If you are interested in speaking to my classes, please click the Apply button below to fill out an application.</p>   
    </div>
     
    <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h3>MSIS 4363</h3>
        <h4>Advanced Application Development</h4>
        <h5>Class Type: In-person</h5>
        <p>	Students in this course learn to develop next-generation, data driven mobile applications involving database development, development of web services, server-side business logic, and XML-based user interface design in format of a capstone project.  </p>
        <h5>Speaker Guidelines</h5>
        <p> I am looking for someone with approximately 5+ years of DevOps experience to speak to my class. They are learning about the continuous development process by using Azure Pipelines, and I would like a speaker who is able to talk about their experience with this process. What portion of your organization uses continuous development? How has this added value to your organization? If you are interested in speaking to my class, please click the Apply button below to fill out an application.  </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row times gx-0">
    <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h4>Class Times</h4>
        <p class="me-3">Tuesday/Thursday 10:30am-11:45am</p>
        <p class="me-3">Online</p>
        <a class="button" asp-page="/RequestApplication">Application <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h4>Class Times</h4>
        <p>Tuesday/Thursday 12:00pm-1:15pm</p>
        <a class="button" asp-page="/RequestApplication">Application <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
    </div>
</div>

   
